# When NO MCP Tool Applies

If none of the above triggers match, proceed with standard file operations (read_file, search_replace, etc). But if there's ANY ambiguity, default to asking the user which tool they prefer.

**Critical Principle:** When a purpose-built MCP tool exists for a task, you MUST use it. General-purpose tools are for tasks that don't fit any MCP category.
